<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0552b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b06">大願惟法忍菩薩也如無量壽四十八願是大願之類</note>
<note n="0552b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b07">海有五德大士亦然一不受毀戒屍二出慧明寶三施法雨不溢四魔邪風日不侵五其智淵深莫測</note>
<note n="0552b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b08">自治而後能治人自治純熟故能方便設教</note>
<note n="0552b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b09">含齒無不敬淨養無不恭故曰供養中最</note>
<note n="0552b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b10">凡人易以威順難以理從故大士每處其尊以弘化長者豪族望重多以世教自居故為說出世間勝法</note>
<note n="0553b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b01">非得菩提心安得此兼善天下乎</note>
<note n="0553b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b02">護世四天王也諸惡鬼神殘食眾生四王護之不令害也</note>
<note n="0553b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b03">欲明履道之身未免斯患況無德而可保耶又曰同我者易信異我者難順故因身疾廣明身患</note>
<note n="0553b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b04">萬事萬行皆四大成在外為土木山河在內為四肢百體聚為生散為死生為內死為外內外雖殊其大不異總明無我也</note>
<note n="0553b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b05">丘井以下總喻生老病死眾苦無量</note>
<note n="0553b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b06">佛身者法身也無生而無不生無形而無不形在天而天在人而人二乘所不識補處所不覩</note>
<note n="0553b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b07">始觀時係心一處名為止靜極則明明即慧慧名觀也止觀定慧</note>
<note n="0553b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b08">收結句有力有神</note>
</p>
